{"tid":686911,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生好絕望","createTime":"2018-06-01T17:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T19:54:43.000Z","uid":22791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8b902d0a90db5376814bc67f6f9b3469dab5a55e","tid":686911,"uid":22791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:15:36.000Z","msg":"我個人生好似玩god of war開撚咗戰神mode咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日做夜做 捱得咁撚辛苦都唔知為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日望住啲客鳩下柒下 飲酒食煙吹水玩女人 r撚爆頭都唔明佢地憑咩咁撚有錢<br />\n唔係普通有錢 係講緊上市集團主席 範範都有撈 飲酒係飲自己酒莊啲酒嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我？捱多100年都捱唔到好似佢地咁<br />\n<br />\n我試過樂觀面對現實 就算諸事不順禍不單行 我都咬關牙關撐過去 以為陳奕迅首歌咁  黑暗過後會是晨曦<br />\n結果？只係變得更加黑暗<br />\n<br />\n連續3日不停做 日日瞓得嗰3 4個鐘 捱到依家病撚埋 企係到成個人係勁暈手震腳震 真係好想死 一了百了 唔洗再俾呢個世界挑逗玩弄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起成日都會有人批鬥自殺既人 笑鳩佢有勇氣自殺冇勇氣生存嗰啲 我依家正式屌哂佢地老母 你冇經歷過人地既生命 根本就冇資格批評人地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有時候，死係一種解脫，脫離呢個名叫「現實」既地獄。</span></span>"},{"pid":"b0be274086e4d3cd7112eae5a496cac41ff670d0","tid":686911,"uid":22791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:27:37.000Z","msg":"屌你連登呢個充滿loser既地方都冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd42aa72f2885a33b68c56cedb4832cbb9463e11","tid":686911,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"做高級食店職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc3ee9dcc939ef36fafcbd8882a5151f6ec56bb","tid":686911,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"轉工吧"},{"pid":"f0ca3911a66447cbe7acfc7ab14ad486691d393c","tid":686911,"uid":22791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd42aa72f288